## Use Case 2: Comprehensive Career Tracking for Entertainment Professionals

### Description
Agents, career analysts, and entertainment professionals need complete career trajectories and filmography data for actors, directors, and producers. This enables portfolio analysis, career planning, and talent management decisions.

### Business Goals
- Compile complete filmography across different roles and genres
- Track career progression and longevity
- Identify professional growth patterns and specializations
- Support talent recruitment and management decisions

### Key Requirements Enabled
- R13, R16, R25: Retrieve names of actors, directors, and producers
- R15: Access complete filmography for any actor (movies they participated in)
- R17: Access directorial work (all movies directed by a specific director)
- R26: Access production work (all movies produced by a specific producer)
- R19, R20, R28, R29: Identify first and last movie for career span analysis
- R23, R24, R32, R33: Determine if professionals have credits in multiple roles

### Example Queries
- "Show me all movies directed by Director X, sorted by year"
- "How many films has Producer Y worked on across different roles (producer, executive, associate)?"
- "What is the career span of Actor Z? (from first to last film)"
- "Which professionals have worked both as directors and actors?"

